
PASSWORD ENCRYPTION

Use tagcmdPassword to encrypt the Yarn API password:

  $ tagcmdPassword.py encrypt

  $ Password to encrypt: *******

The script will provide a config line to add to unravel.properties

If you want to test a decrypt use:

  $ tagcmdPassword.py decrypt <encrypted password>



UNRAVEL PROPERTIES
------------------

Define the following properties as appropriate the environment

	tagcmdpy.yarn.api.password=<encrypted password from tagcmdPassword.py encrypt >
	tagcmdpy.yarn.api.user=<Ambari User with API access>
	tagcmdpy.yarn.api.host=<Ambari host>
	tagcmdpy.yarn.api.port=<Ambari Port>
	tagcmdpy.yarn.api.ssl=<False=http / True = https>
